title: Classic Rock Gold Hits 2 CD mp3
description:
Uploaded by Bl4ze428. 320 kbps   Have fun and thank you for helping share with the community. Classic Rock Gold is a two-disc compilation album released in 2005. It features thirty-three of the greatest hits to come out of classic rock, many of which are from the Universal Music Group catalogue.
It features Whitesnake, Lynyrd Skynyrd, Steppenwolf, Scorpions, Joe Walsh, Rod Stewart, and Peter Frampton
